# Generated code and hive artefacts (ledger, metrics, LOOP.md).
workspace/

# Secrets. HIVE_PROVIDER=anthropic needs ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, and the single most
# common way to leak an API key is to put it in a file next to the code that
# reads it and then forget. These are ignored before they exist, not after.
.env
.env.*
.anthropic_key
*.key
